## Page Object Conventions

- All Page Objects extend `BasePage`
- Name classes after the screen/module identifier (e.g. `PRL300Q`, `RSS310Q`)
- Declare all locators as `private readonly` class fields
- Expose **business-oriented** methods (`submitInvoice()` not `clickButton3()`)
- Wrap test actions in `test.step()` for narrative Playwright report output

### Adding a new Page Object

```bash
# Create src/pages/<Module>/<ScreenCode>.ts
# Extend BasePage, define locators, add action methods
```

